==Chinese==

===Etymology===
Literally: big similarities, small differences.

===Pronunciation===
====[[wikipedia:Standard_Mandarin|Mandarin]]====
[[Pinyin]]: dà tóng xĭao yì
====[[wikipedia:Min Nan|Min Nan]]====
[[wikipedia:POJ|POJ]]: tāi-tông-sió-ī

===Idiom===
'''[[大]][[同]][[小]][[异]]''' ([[Simplified Chinese]])

# Almost the same; almost identical; similar in most respects.

===Alternate forms===
[[大]][[同]][[小]][[異]] ([[Traditional Chinese]])

